CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 26, 1941, pg. 1, reads: "For Bill! - Among the most enthusiastic supporters of the Health Clinic bill was Mrs. Steina Mae Fish, pictured in Council last Monday with an imposing sign perched on her hat advocating the clinic. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men and women, some holding signs inscribed "We Want the Clinic Give it to Us," in Pittsburgh City Council building
